                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-394" type="given" value="HENRY JOHN"></interp>HENRY JOHN SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. The prisoner is coachman to my father, George Smith, who lives at Friern Barnet—I believe these articles to be my father's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PAYNE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Has the prisoner a wife and family? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, four children.</p>
